Comic True Mono — licensing
Copyright (c) 2026 The Comic True Mono Authors

This project is licensed in two parts:

  1. The FONTS (fonts/ttf/*.ttf, and the master they are generated from) are
     licensed under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1 — see OFL.txt.
     They incorporate outlines from Comic Relief, which is itself OFL 1.1, and
     the OFL requires derivative fonts to stay under the OFL.

  2. The BUILD SCRIPTS (everything under sources/, EXCEPT the vendored font
     binaries in sources/vendor/) are licensed under the MIT License, printed
     below. They contain no third-party outlines.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Fonts this software is built from
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The font incorporates or is derived from the following projects. Their
copyright and permission notices are retained here as required by their
respective licenses.

  Comic Relief
    Copyright 2013 The Comic Relief Project Authors
    https://github.com/loudifier/Comic-Relief          (SIL OFL 1.1)
    — Cyrillic (U+0400–04FF) and Greek (U+0370–03FF), fitted to the mono cell.
      Its OFL license is the reason the fonts ship under the OFL; see OFL.txt.

  Comic Shanns
    Original work Copyright (c) 2018 Shannon Miwa
    https://github.com/shannpersand/comic-shanns        (MIT)
    — root source of the letterforms; Latin, accented Latin (Latin-1 Supplement,
      Latin Extended-A/B), punctuation, arrows, currency, math operators.

  Comic Mono
    Modified work Copyright (c) 2019 dtinth
    https://github.com/dtinth/comic-mono-font           (MIT)
    — monospace base (Regular/Bold), advance width 1116 @ UPM 2048.

  Serious Shanns
    Modified work Copyright (c) 2023-2024 Kyle Beechly
    https://github.com/kaBeech/serious-shanns           (MIT)
    — source of the lambda glyph and the hand-drawn Italic / Bold Italic masters.

  comic-shanns (fork by clsn)
    https://github.com/clsn/comic-shanns                (MIT)
    — additional characters: Æ æ Œ œ Þ þ ſ ƿ Ƿ ꝛ ∀ ∃ ∄.

  comic-shanns (fork by lilmayu)
    https://github.com/lilmayu/comic-shanns             (MIT)
    — corrected caron/háček diacritics: Č č Ď Ě ě Ň ň Ř ř Š š Ť Ž ž and U+02C7.

MIT permits including its material in an OFL work, so the MIT-licensed outlines
above are redistributed within the OFL fonts with their notices retained.

